image_analysis.description: A photograph of an FBI evidence placard being held against a white door with gold trim. Two hands wearing black nitrile gloves are visible; the left hand holds the top corner of the paper, and the right hand holds a small blue and black object (possibly a marker or evidence tool) near the bottom left of the paper.
image_analysis.layout: The evidence placard is centered on a door. The placard contains printed fields with handwritten information. A black redaction box covers the photographer's name.
